# Complete Page List for CRM System

Based on your requirements, here is the **complete page structure** for the frontend:

---

## 📁 AUTHENTICATION MODULE

| Page | Route | Description |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Login | `/login` | User authentication with email/password |
| Register | `/register` | New user registration |
| Forgot Password | `/forgot-password` | Password reset request |
| Reset Password | `/reset-password` | Set new password with token |
| Two-Factor Auth | `/2fa` | Optional 2FA verification |

---

## 📁 DASHBOARD MODULE

| Page | Route | Description |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Main Dashboard | `/dashboard` | KPI overview, key figures, charts |
| Company Selector | `/dashboard/company-switch` | Switch between 3 companies |
| Daily Key Figures | `/dashboard/key-figures` | Revenue, costs, utilization, contribution margins |

---

## 📁 COMPANY MANAGEMENT MODULE

| Page | Route | Description |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Company Overview | `/companies` | List all 3 companies |
| Company Details | `/companies/[id]` | Edit company settings |
| Company Logo Settings | `/companies/[id]/logo` | Upload/change logo (future independent logos) |
| Invoice Number Settings | `/companies/[id]/invoice-numbers` | Configure consecutive invoice numbering |

