## 🎯 MVP PRIORITY PAGES (First Release)

For your **initial working version**, focus on these **30 core pages**:

### Phase 1 - Foundation (Week 1-2)
1. `/login` - Login
2. `/register` - Register
3. `/dashboard` - Dashboard
4. `/companies` - Company selection
5. `/users` - User management

### Phase 2 - Core Business (Week 3-4)
6. `/customers` - Customer list
7. `/customers/create` - Create cus\tomer
8. `/suppliers` - Supplier list
9. `/materials` - Material list
10. `/services` - Service list

### Phase 3 - Orders & Offers (Week 5-6)
11. `/orders` - Order list
12. `/orders/create` - Create order
13. `/orders/import-pdf` - PDF import
14. `/offers` - Offer list
15. `/offers/create` - Create offer with checklist
16. `/offers/[id]/convert-to-order` - Convert to order

### Phase 4 - Invoicing (Week 7)
17. `/invoices` - Invoice list
18. `/invoices/create` - Create invoice
19. `/invoices/approval` - Approval workflow

### Phase 5 - Scheduling (Week 8)
20. `/calendar` - Calendar view
21. `/calendar/schedule` - Schedule view
22. `/calendar/crew-view` - Crew view

### Phase 6 - Crews (Week 9)
23. `/crews` - Crew list
24. `/crews/create` - Create crew
25. `/crews/settlements` - Crew settlements

### Phase 7 - Reporting & Settings (Week 10)
26. `/reports/key-figures` - Key figures
27. `/settings` - General settings
28. `/profile` - User profile
29. `/import` - Data import
30. `/communication/whatsapp` - WhatsApp integration

